                  </persName>
            . I was at the adjoining house, and saw the prisoner get in at the window; I gave an alarm to Thompson, and he was pursued - he ran through the garden where these tongs were found.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280703-81-person575">
                  SOPHIA 
                  HAZLE
               <interp inst="t18280703-81-person575" type="surname" value="HAZLE"></interp>
